{"tid":2133580,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"賓在九巴中針你","createTime":"2020-07-31T07:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T10:05:15.000Z","uid":72497,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fe047c4d2aa07bb0f6f4fc3c4c1ec1d7e6013f1e","tid":2133580,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:31:47.000Z","msg":"n賓的　這一針　哪個可比<br />\n你上車  差一些　永遠不起<br />\n邂逅愛滋場地　注定是好戲<br />\n針自何處插起<br />\n<br />\n賓緊張　蠢蠢的    欠缺兇器<br />\n賓輕鬆　輕輕的　放下針器<br />\n特拿來的時候　 是拿着針筒<br />\n他走了　便遺下了針十數支<br />\n<br />\n*如果每個座位  全部插着你<br />\n連遇上亦要躲避<br />\n無非想放下你　還是插實你<br />\n誰又再贈送傷悲<br />\n前事最怕有人提起　就算n賓出力推搪<br />\n我們也知道佢嚟<br />\n<br />\n你太遠　賓想緊　怎去針你<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG17hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=cf5fca42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網 <br />\n你太近　一坐底　血已高飛<br />\n路程也許太短　似場流星雨<br />\n一眨眼　就如幻覺血又濺起<br />\n<br />\nRepeat ＊(＊)<br />\n<br />\n佢還在九巴中針你   <br />\n佢遺下愛滋針針你"},{"pid":"33afbf4e49b8581e1cf9494f150be884674ab66c","tid":2133580,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774b4fc4269e110c2066b9d6b371ea1cbe6d25ca","tid":2133580,"uid":241543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:32:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad14d4e30c6221e8ff05a56ebbc304ec28d5281f","tid":2133580,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:33:28.000Z","msg":"針在九巴中賓你"},{"pid":"5984f64099947057e4570f081542fdc2be94c23c","tid":2133580,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"774b4fc4269e110c2066b9d6b371ea1cbe6d25ca","tid":2133580,"uid":241543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:32:33.000